Coming off another winning week Colin gives his Blazing 5 picks from week 16 to RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree with. Plus, Colin releases TWO bonus picks that were not included in his Blazing 5.
